OL,3,CShoplifter who tried to jump off of
OL,4,Cpier to escape police jailed
OL,6,FBodycam footage from Kent Police shows
OL,7,Fthe moment an officer arrested Michael
OL,8,FThompson
OL,10,FA prolific shoplifter who tried to
OL,11,Fescape police by jumping off a pier
OL,12,Fhas been jailed.
OL,14,FMichael Thompson, of Trafalgar Street
OL,15,Fin Gillingham, was arrested following
OL,16,Fa series of thefts at the BP petrol
OL,17,Fstation in Maidstone, between 2 May
OL,18,Fand 6 July 2025.
