OL,3,CShoplifter who tried to jump off of
OL,4,Cpier to escape police jailed
OL,6,FKent Police identified Thompson from
OL,7,FCCTV footage, and on 14 July, he was
OL,8,Fspotted on the Chatham high street.
OL,10,FHe was then chased by officers and was
OL,11,Feventually detained when he tried to
OL,12,Fclimb over railings on Sun Pier.
OL,14,FThe 37-year-old pleaded guilty before
OL,15,FMedway Magistrates' Court and was
OL,16,Fjailed for 25 weeks.
OL,18,FThe time he will serve includes a
OL,19,Fsanction for breaching a suspended
OL,20,Fsentence.
