OL,6,FThompson will also have to pay #442 in
OL,7,Fcompensation.
OL,9,FInspector Paul Diddams said: 'Our
OL,10,Fneighbourhood officers are committed
OL,11,Fto identifying and arresting those
OL,12,Fsuspected of persistently targeting
OL,13,Four local businesses.
OL,15,F"Anyone who is brought into custody
OL,16,Fand charged with multiple offences by
OL,17,Four investigators should expect to be
OL,18,Fplaced immediately before the court.
